data.description: Welcome home to this newly constructed beauty! Located near Downtown Commerce, dining, and shopping. This kitchen features all new Samsung appliances and an island perfect for entertaining with view to the family room. You will also get a covered patio on the massive backyard. A Spacious Master's suite comes complete with vaulted ceilings, walk-in closet, tile shower and double vanity. Welcome home!
